Nintendo to Cut U.S. Price of 3DS Game Player to $170

-- B y   G e a r o i d   R e i d y
-- 
2011-07-28T07:56:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/nintendo-to-cut-u-s-price-of-3ds-game-player-to-170-correct-.html
(Corrects source of company statement.)  Nintendo Co. will cut the retail
price of its 3DS handheld game player in the U.S. to $169.99
from $249.99 starting Aug. 12, according to a statement on its
website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gearoid Reidy at 
 greidy1@bloomberg.net  